content.rendered:
We have some good news for you! In cooperation with MPSocial, one of the most popular social media forums, we decided to give out Jarvee licenses for free! If you participate in the contest, you have a chance to win some of the prizes!

This forum is the place where you can meet many Jarvee users, as some of the most interesting and most informative conversations are going on there. You can share your experience with other participants, ask questions, and start discussions. This doesn’t have to be only Jarvee related, you can talk about anything related to Social Media, Digital Marketing, SEO, earning online, and similar areas.

If you are interested to hear how you can participate and what you can win, check it out here. Good luck!
